Definition: emotionlessly and heartlessly
Example: with deliberate cruelty or callousness; he cold-bloodedly planned the murder of his boss
Synonyms: adj, all, inhumane, cold-blooded, in_cold_blood, emotionlessly, and, heartlessly, with, deliberate, cruelty, or, callousness, he, planned, the, murder, of, his, boss
Category: adv.all
